11. Success Metrics

1,000 registered users in 3 months

10% Pro conversion rate

Stable performance under 5,000 concurrent users

12. Development Approach Using AI Agent (Cursor)

You will:

Feed this PRD into Cursor AI

Build feature by feature

Generate code in modules

Review architecture carefully

Never generate entire system at once

Implement incrementally